{"tid":1680507,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彭博：對習近平而言 中共四中全會的重點 掌權比經濟重要","createTime":"2019-10-29T01:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T07:05:05.000Z","uid":155095,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"53a412ecda1e2c4ab7e1e86cfce143d4f1999fb0","tid":1680507,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T01:00:42.000Z","msg":"source: <a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/m/article/breakingnews/2960101\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2960101&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFP0XpujcHphTkFDN4g7DGnHE%3D&h=e6a33269\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2960101&h=60c1d597\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/m/article/breakingnews/2960101</a><br />\n<br />\n中共「千呼萬喚始出來」的「第十九屆四中全會」終於在28日起召開，面對中國1年多來內外交迫的經濟壓力，外界關注中共是否會作出重大政策決定，<span style=\"color: red;\">然而《彭博》報導指出，對中共總書記習近平而言，能不能牢牢抓緊權力、控制國家政經，仍是比中國經濟更重要的事情。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D1SpQfSU8AItDos.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FD1SpQfSU8AItDos.jpg&h=c989e8be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於四中全會，中國官媒曾表示，中共將持續「為堅持並改善中國特色社會主義的治理、加強對中國體制及治理能力作出努力」；《彭博》引述中國研究機構Trivium China的說法指出，基於習近平對「體制」的定義，恐怕涵蓋廣泛，<span style=\"color: red;\">包含整個黨對經濟、社會、文化等等的全方位控制。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D9j8qZlU4AAwuFX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FD9j8qZlU4AAwuFX.jpg&h=9c6e7dac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n按以往慣例，中共要在三中全會討論經濟問題，然而本屆中共中央召開的二、三中全會，都是為了討論「政治」，也就是有關修憲取消國家主席任期制的議題，自那時以來，<span style=\"color: red;\">中共已1年又8個月未召開全會，是1978年改革開放以來最長的間隔</span>，因此部份專家期待本次全會將聚焦於經濟改革、穩定及開放等議題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.peoplenews.tw/news/8ab46bfb-75f9-4159-a4ec-899f7597fdd2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.peoplenews.tw%2Fnews%2F8ab46bfb-75f9-4159-a4ec-899f7597fdd2.jpg&h=2534b76e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然而經濟學人智庫（Economist Intelligence Unit）首席中國經濟學家任韜（Tom Rafferty）事先打預防針，表示儘管外界期待本次全會能提供更清晰的2020年經濟展望，但不應期望太高，<span style=\"color: red;\">明年的中國經濟展望，本次全會可能給不了答案。</span>"},{"pid":"258c8e96ae671fc77ea84aafd0d9f3fc7c2a2ddb","tid":1680507,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T01:01:34.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f71230ef313732bf32564c84e9950667348bc806","tid":1680507,"uid":83523,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T01:05:16.000Z","msg":"即係講到出口寧願要全民食草<br />\n<br />\n都唔比亡黨"},{"pid":"b588f54db86b19e8cc67ea6a0bd9454cf59fc39c","tid":1680507,"uid":48623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f71230ef313732bf32564c84e9950667348bc806","tid":1680507,"uid":83523,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T01:05:16.000Z","msg":"即係講到出口寧願要全民食草<br />\n<br />\n都唔比亡黨"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T01:09:59.000Z","msg":"所以話小學程度無錯<br />\n支那人有得食就唔會反抗，佢連屎都無得比人民食又點維穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa01f8bc41d64835bb9ff50875b4b5098acdaec","tid":1680507,"uid":155095,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f71230ef313732bf32564c84e9950667348bc806","tid":1680507,"uid":83523,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T01:05:16.000Z","msg":"即係講到出口寧願要全民食草<br />\n<br />\n都唔比亡黨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T02:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D6N1MM5UwAAk8Nq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FD6N1MM5UwAAk8Nq.jpg&h=b845b9f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Dn0_f-BXkAEORme.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpb